#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kpat.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KPat (aka KPatience) is a relaxing card sorting game. To win the game a "
"player has to arrange a single deck of cards in certain order amongst each "
"other."
msgstr ""
"KPat, KPatience bezala ere ezaguna, kartak sailkatzeko karta-joko lasaigarri "
"bat da. Jokoa irabazteko, jokalariak karta-sorta bakar bat karten "
"elkarrekiko hurrenkera jakin batean antolatu behar du."

